aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20who%20lost%20her%20son%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20complained%20of%20severe%20stomach%20ache%20and%20difficulty%20to%20open%20his%20eyes.%20He%20said%20he%20had%20consumed%20arrack.%20Initially%2C%20the%20hospital%20refused%20to%20admit%20him%2C%20saying%20he's%20drunk.%20The%20state%20government%20should%20shut%20down%20all%20liquor%20shops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20mother%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMy%20son%20suffered%20excruciating%20stomach%20pain.%20He%20could%20neither%20see%20nor%20hear.%20This%20shouldn't%20happen%20to%20anyone.%20Stop%20selling%20liquor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20arrested%20four%20suspected%20bootleggers%20and%20detained%2010%20others.%20Confirming%20that%20these%20deaths%20were%20caused%20due%20to%20consumption%20of%20toxic%20liquor%2C%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%20told%20NDTV%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20investigating%20what%20exactly%20they%20consumed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20suspended%20district%20police%20chief%20Samay%20Singh%20Meena%20and%20appointed%20Rajat%20Chaturvedi%20in%20his%20place.%20Collector%20Sravan%20Kumar%20Jatavath%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20MS%20Prasanth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police-rank%20officer%20of%20prohibition%20enforcement%20wing%2C%20three%20inspectors%20and%20as%20many%20sub-inspectors%20were%20also%20suspended.%C2%A0The%20state%20government%20also%20transferred%20the%20probe%20into%20the%20toxic%20liquor%20tragedy%20to%20CB-CID.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20he%20is%20shocked%20and%20pained%20about%20the%20loss%20of%20lives.%20%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20have%20been%20arrested.%20Action%20has%20been%20taken%20against%20officials%20who%20failed%20to%20prevent%20this.%20We%20will%20crack%20down%20with%20an%20iron%20hand.%20If%20public%20complain%20about%20such%20perpetrators%2C%20action%20would%20be%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20has%20announced%20an%20inquiry%20by%20Justice%20(retd)%20B%20Gokuldas%2C%20a%20retired%20judge%20of%20Madras%20High%20Court.%20A%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20families%20of%20each%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Stalin%20had%20ordered%20the%20arrest%20of%20illegal%20liquor%20brewers%2C%20methanol%20seller%20and%20destruction%20of%20methanol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20tragedy%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20huge%20failure%20by%20intelligence%20agencies%20and%20the%20prohibition%20enforcement%20wing.%20Last%20year%2C%20too%2C%2022%20people%20died%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20after%20consuming%20methanol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Madras%20High%20Court%20yesterday%20pulled%20up%20the%20state%20government%20over%20the%20hooch%20tragedy%2C%20which%20has%20claimed%2055%20lives.%20How%20did%20you%20let%20it%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20citing%20last%20year's%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIADMK%20chief%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly%20Edappadi%20K%20Palaniswami%20slammed%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20for%20and%20said%20the%20state%20government%20failed%20to%20curb%20the%20toxic%20liquor%20problem%20even%20after%20he%20pointed%20out.%20%26quot%3BI%20urge%20Chief%20Minister%20M%20K%20Stalin%20to%20take%20stringent%20action%20to%20curb%20toxic%20liquor%20instead%20of%20word%20play%20like%20last%20time%2C%20when%20they%20called%20it%20methanol%20and%20not%20toxic%20liquor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20BJP%20chief%20K%20Annamalai%20said%20DMK%20had%20not%20%26quot%3Blearnt%20its%20lesson%26quot%3B%20after%2022%20deaths%20due%20to%20consumption%20of%20toxic%20liquor%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719027840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5ph5vbb_tamil-nadu-hooch_625x300_22_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftamil-nad