2C%20however%2C%20acquitted%20them%20of%20a%20more%20serious%20charge%20of%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindujas%2C%20whose%20fortunes%20are%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%20%2447%20billion%2C%20run%20businesses%20ranging%20from%20oil%20and%20gas%20to%20banking%20and%20healthcare%20in%20as%20many%20as%2038%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trial%2C%20prosecutors%20had%20alleged%20the%20Hindujas%20paid%20their%20staff%20only%20%248%20(Rs%20660)%20for%20working%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20a%20day.%20This%20was%20less%20than%20a%20tenth%20of%20the%20wage%20mandated%20by%20Swiss%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20also%20confiscated%20the%20passports%20of%20their%20staff%20and%20rarely%20allowed%20them%20outside%20their%20villa%20in%20the%20wealthy%20neighbourhood%20of%20Cologny%2C%20the%20prosecutors%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20family%20spent%20more%20on%20their%20dog%20than%20on%20their%20servants.%20Their%20expenses%20were%20around%208%2C584%20Swiss%20francs%20(Rs%208%20lakh)%20on%20their%20dog%20every%20year%20whereas%20some%20of%20their%20staff%20worked%20up%20to%2018%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20for%20just%207%20Swiss%20francs%20(Rs%20660)%20per%20day%2C%20Swiss%20prosecutor%20Yves%20Bertossa%20had%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindujas%20had%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20their%20employees%20could%20freely%20leave%20the%20villa%20and%20received%20ample%20benefits.%20The%20defence%20argued%20that%20the%20staff%20was%20%26quot%3Bgrateful%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Hindujas%20for%20%26quot%3Boffering%20them%20a%20better%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bappalled%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20verdict%20and%20have%20filed%20a%20challenge%20in%20a%20higher%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20appalled%20and%20disappointed%20by%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20decision%20made%20in%20this%20court%20of%20first%20instance%2C%20and%20we%20have%20of%20course%20filed%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20higher%20court%20thereby%20making%20this%20part%20of%20the%20judgment%20not%20effective%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20statement%20signed%20by%20the%20lawyers%20of%20the%20Hindujas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindujas%20had%20earlier%20reached%20an%20out-of-court%20settlement%20with%20the%20three%20employees%20who%20had%20made%20the%20accusations%20against%20them%2C%20but%20the%20prosecution%20went%20ahead%20with%20it%20due%20to%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakash%20and%20Kamal%20Hinduja%2C%20both%20in%20their%2070s%2C%20did%20not%20attend%20the%20court%20due%20to%20health%20reasons.%20Ajay%20and%20Namrata%20had%20attended%20the%20trial%20but%20were%20not%20present%20on%20Friday%20to%20hear%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719023340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fekal4go8_prakash-hinduja_625x300_19_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwhy-the-hindujas-uks-wealthiest-family-face-jail-term-in-switzerland-5942979%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindujas%2C%20the%20wealthiest%20family%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20face%20around%20four-year%20jail%20terms%20for%20exploiting%20their%20Indian%20employees%20at%20their%20Geneva%20villa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwhy-the-hindujas-uks-wealthiest-family-face-jail-term-in-switzerland-5942979%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwhy-the-hindujas-uks-wealthiest-family-face-jail-term-in-switzerland-5942979%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fwhy-the-hindujas-uks-wealthiest-family-face-jail-term-in-switzerland-5942979%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sara%20gets%20teary%20eyed%20talking%20about%20