istent-and-clear-says-mea%2Farticleshow%2F111180408.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findias-position-on-dalai-lama-consistent-and-clear-says-mea%2Farticleshow%2F111180408.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI'm%20Not%20Happy%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Coach's%20Blockbuster%20Take%20On%20Kohli's%20Lean%20T20%20WC%20Run%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cchallenged%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20ongoing%20T20%20World%20Cup%20but%20his%20lean%20run%20is%20allowing%20the%20less%20experienced%20players%20to%20step%20up%20and%20contribute%20to%20the%20team's%20cause%2C%20India%20batting%20coach%20Vikram%20Rathour%20said%20on%20Friday.%20India%20outplayed%20Afghanistan%20at%20the%20Kensington%20Oval%20here%20on%20Thursday%20to%20make%20a%20perfect%20start%20to%20their%20Super%208s%20campaign.%20However%2C%20Kohli%20was%20tested%20once%20again%20in%20the%20powerplay%20and%20ended%20up%20with%20a%20run-a-ball%2024%2C%20his%20first%20double%20digit%20score%20in%20the%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI'm%20not%20happy.%20I%20would%20love%20it%20if%20he%20gets%20going%20and%20scores%20more%20runs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rathour%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20team's%20unbeaten%20run%20in%20the%20event%20without%20Kohli's%20contribution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20yeah%2C%20it%20is%20good%20when%20you%20are%20challenged%20at%20times.%20You%20know%2C%20the%20guys%20who%20are%20not%20getting%20too%20much%20of%20batting%20in%20India%20sometimes%2C%20they%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20put%20up%20scores%20today%20and%20our%20middle-order%20came%20to%20play.%20So%2C%20it%20was%20good%20to%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20Pant%20was%20impressive%20while%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20took%20the%20game%20away%20from%20Afghanistan%20with%20a%20sublime%20fi