%20involved%20in%20committing%20the%20offence%2C%20he%20will%20face%20imprisonment%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20three%20years%2C%20which%20can%20go%20up%20to%2010%20years%2C%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20examination%20authority%20or%20the%20service%20provider%20commits%20an%20organised%20crime%2C%20the%20jail%20term%20will%20be%20a%20minimum%20of%20five%20years%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%2010%2C%20and%20the%20fine%20will%20remain%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notification%20mentions%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20but%20adds%20that%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20will%20remain%20in%20effect%20until%20it%20is%20implemented.%20The%20Sanhita%20and%20the%20other%20criminal%20laws%20are%20scheduled%20to%20come%20into%20effect%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EControversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses%2C%20which%20is%20also%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20on%20May%205.%20The%20results%20were%20announced%20on%20June%204%2C%2010%20days%20before%20schedule%2C%20but%20allegations%20of%20a%20question%20paper%20leak%20and%20grace%20marks%20to%20over%201%2C500%20students%20triggered%20protests.%20Cases%20were%20also%20filed%20in%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20rapped%20the%20NTA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20had%20cancelled%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20just%20a%20day%20after%20it%20was%20held.%20Over%209%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20exam%2C%20which%20is%20held%20for%20Assistant%20Professor%20posts%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%20and%20to%20determine%20eligibility%20for%20junior%20research%20fellowships.%20Addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Education%20Minister%20Pradhan%20said%20the%20UGC%20chairman%20had%20received%20information%20from%20the%20cyber%20crime%20team%20in%20the%20home%20ministry%20about%20questions%20being%20on%20the%20darknet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20described%20allegations%20of%20leaks%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20medical%20paper%20and%20others%20as%20isolated%20incidents%20but%20said%20he%20takes%20moral%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%2C%20strengthened%20after%20its%20much-improved%20showing%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20has%20attacked%20the%20government%20over%20the%20issue%20and%20it%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20brought%20up%20in%20Parliament%20when%20the%20session%20begins%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719020280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-05%2Ft8io71hg_omr-sheet_625x300_01_May_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-paper-leak-law-notified-amid-exam-mess-jail-term-fine-up-to-a-crore-5941544%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20an%20important%20step%20amid%20the%20controversies%20surrounding%20the%20NEET%20and%20UGC-NET%20exams%2C%20the%20Centre%20has%20notified%20a%20stringent%20law%20that%20was%20passed%20in%20February%20to%20prevent%20paper%20leaks%20and%20cheating.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-paper-leak-law-notified-amid-exam-mess-jail-term-fine-up-to-a-crore-5941544%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-paper-leak-law-notified-amid-exam-mess-jail-term-fine-up-to-a-crore-5941544%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanti-paper-leak-law-notified-amid-exam-mess-jail-term-fine-up-to-a-crore-5941544%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Red%20Cross%20says%2022%20killed%20in%20strike%20near%20its%20Gaza%20office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719020026000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.