en%20with%20limited%20power%20and%20no%20WiFi%20connection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECat%20accessibility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20prioritized%20feeders%20with%20wide%2C%20shallow%20bowls%20free%20of%20obstacles%2C%20such%20as%20a%20food%20dispenser%20jutting%20out%20from%20above%20the%20bowl%20or%20narrow%20openings.%20An%20open%20feeding%20area%2C%20like%20the%20one%20offered%20by%20our%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Feeder%20Robot%2C%20allows%20cats%20to%20approach%20the%20bowl%20comfortably%20and%20eat%20without%20feeling%20trapped.%20Feeders%20with%20cordless%20designs%20and%20long-lasting%20batteries%20provide%20more%20placement%20options%2C%20further%20reducing%20mealtime%20stress%20for%20skittish%20cats%2C%20especially%20in%20multi-cat%20households.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumber%20of%20daily%20meals%20and%20customization%20of%20meal%20size%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20ranked%20the%20feeders%20by%20the%20number%20of%20meals%20they%20can%20dispense%20in%20a%20day%20and%20the%20size%20of%20those%20meals.%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Following%20the%20manufacturer's%20instructions%2C%20we%20disassembled%20and%20washed%20each%20feeder%20after%20two%20weeks%20of%20testing%2C%20evaluating%20any%20challenges%20with%20disassembly%2C%20reassembly%2C%20or%20cleaning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20are%20quiet%20beyond%20the%20natural%20clatter%20of%20kibble%20in%20the%20bowl.%20Watson%20emphasizes%20the%20importance%20of%20quiet%20operation%2C%20especially%20for%20timid%20cats.%20Loud%2C%20sudden%20noises%20can%20startle%20cats%20with%20sensitive%20hearing%2C%20she%20says.%20To%20evaluate%20noise%20levels%20objectively%2C%20we%20used%20a%20%26quot%3BSound%20Meter%26quot%3B%20app%20to%20record%20the%20average%20decibel%20rating%20during%20each%20feeder's%20dispensing%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20cat%20parents%2C%20we%20understand%20the%20persistence%20of%20a%20hungry%20cat.%20To%20assess%20durability%2C%20we%20simulated%20a%20food-motivated%20cat's%20attempts%20to%20breach%20the%20feeder%20by%20using%20a%20fork%20to%20try%20to%20pry%20open%20the%20lid%20with%20moderate%20pressure.%20For%20feeders%20with%20rotating%20food%20compartments%2C%20we%20used%20a%20fork%20to%20attempt%20to%20pull%20the%20next%20meal%20toward%20the%20dispensing%20opening.%20Lastly%2C%20for%20vertical%20feeders%2C%20we%20pushed%20them%20over%20three%20times%20to%20check%20if%20food%20spilled%20out%20or%20if%20the%20hopper%20or%20bowl%20detached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20key%20evaluation%20criteria%2C%20we%20considered%20the%20cost%2C%20footprint%2C%20warranty%2C%20and%20customer%20service%20associated%20with%20each%20feeder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EAutomatic%20cat%20feeder%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20giving%20your%20cat%20meals%20yourself%20can%20help%20strengthen%20your%20bond%20and%20food%20puzzle%20feeders%20can%20provide%20mental%20enrichment%2C%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20ensure%20your%20cat%20receives%20regular%20meals%20in%20precise%20portions.%20These%20feeders%20are%20often%20beneficial%20if%20you're%20not%20home%20or%20have%20mobility%20limitations%20that%20restrict%20your%20feeding%20routine.%20Feeders%20that%20can%20recognize%20individual%20cats%2C%20such%20as%20the%20SureFeed%20Microchip%20Pet%20Feeder%20Connect%2C%20can%20even%20keep%20other%20pets%20from%20stealing%20from%20other%20bowls.%20Vets%20often%20recommend%20automatic%20feeders%20for%20these%20reasons%2C%20Krohn%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20continuous%20cat%20feeder%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWatson%20recommends%20mimicking%20a%20cat's%20natural%20eating%20patterns%20by%20feeding%20them%20several%20small%20meals%20throughout%20the%20day%20%E2%80%94%20ideally%20at%20least%20five.%20%26quot%3BCats%20spend%20up%20to%2070%25%20of%20their%20daily%20activities%20on%20feeding-related%20behaviors%20and%20hunting%20for%20food%20no%20matter%20how%20well-fed%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20Our%20best%20overall%20pick%2C%20the%20Whisker%20Feeder-Robot%2C%20dispenses%20up%20to%20eight%20meals%20a%20day%20in%20portions%20as%20small%20as%201%2F8%20cup.%20It%20also%20offers%20a%20gravity-feed%20option%20for%20continuous%20dispensing.%20The%20more%20economical%20Petlibro%20Granary%20Camera%20Feeder%20can%20dispense%20up%20to%2010%20meals%20daily%20in%20portions%20as%20small%20as%20about%20a%20tablespoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20cat%20feeder%20for%20traveling%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20we%20tested%2C%20the%20Petlibro%20Air%20is%20a%20budget-friendly%20option%20with%20a%20small%20footprint%20that%20makes%20it%20ideal%20for%20packing.%20It%20does%20have%20the%20smallest%20food%20capacity%2C%20but%20the%208.5-cup%20hopper%20provides%20ample%20food%20storage%20for%20two%20weeks%20or%20more%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20cat's%20portion%20sizes.%20The%20Petlibro%20Air%20also%20offers%20a%20battery%20backup%20option%20and%20doesn't%20require%20WiFi%20connectivity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20choose%20an%20automatic%20cat%20feeder%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20choosing%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeder%20for%20your%20home%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%20your%20cat's%20needs%20as%20well%20as%20your%20priorities.%20Khorn%20recommends%20features%20that%20promote%20healthy%20eating%20habits%2C%20like%20precise%20portion%20control%20and%20scheduling%20to%20avoid%20overfeeding%20or%20missed%20meals.%20Durability%20is%20also%20key%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20features%20that%20deter%20food-motivated%20cats%20from%20extra%20snacking%2C%20like%20two-handed%20opening%20mechanisms%20or%20microchip%2FRFID%20tag%20access.%20Watson%20says%20some%20cats%20have%20special%20needs%2C%20so%20paying%20attention%20to%20your%20cat's%20eating%20habits%20can%20help%20you%20discover%20their%20preferences.%20Some%20cats%20may%20do%20better%20with%20an%20elevated%20feeder%2C%20a%20quiet%20feeder%2C%20or%20one%20that%20has%20a%20wide%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20automatic%20food%20dispenser%20for%20multiple%20cats%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20feeders%20with%20two%20bowls%20may%20seem%20like%20a%20great%20solution%20for%20multi-cat%20households%2C%20many%20experts%20advise%20against%20them.%20Feeding%20cats%20too%20closely%20together%20can%20trigger%20territorial%20behavior%20and%20anxiety.%20Watson%20says%20cats%20might%20block%20access%20to%20the%20food%2C%20leading%20to%20social%20conflict.%20With%20its%20small%20footprint%20and%20wallet-friendly%20price%2C%20the%20Petlibro%20Air%20Automatic%20Feeder%20may%20be%20a%20great%20option%20for%20multi-cat%20homes.%20Buying%20multiple%20feeders%20and%20placing%20them%20around%20your%20home%20can%20reduce%20competition%20and%20increase%20natural%20foraging%20behaviors.%20The%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20for%20households%20with%20enthusiastic%20eaters%20or%20cats%20on%20special%20diets%20may%20be%20microchip%20or%20RFID%20feeders%2C%20like%20the%20SureFeed%20Microchip%20Pet%20Feeder%20Connect.%20This%20type%20of%20feeder%20only%20allows%20registered%20cats%20to%20access%20the%20food%20bowl.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20I%20feed%20my%20cat%20wet%20food%20while%20away%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EReditic%20recommends%20Closer%20Pet's%20line%20of%20ice%20pack%20feeders%2C%20like%20the%20Cat%20Mate%20C500%205%20Meal%20Digital%20Automatic%20Feeder%2C%20for%20feeding%20cats%20wet%20food%20at%20scheduled%20times.%20This%20feeder%20uses%20a%20cat-proof%20carousel%20and%20ice%20packs%20to%20keep%20up%20to%20four%20pre-scheduled%20meals%20chilled%20and%20has%20one%20open%20compartment%20for%20immediate%20serving.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20the%20brand%20advises%20against%20storing%20wet%20food%20for%20extended%20periods%20in%20hot%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Litter-Robot%20Feeder-Robot%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20black%20and%20white%20Litter-Robot%20Feeder-Robot%20cat%20feeder%20with%20a%20control%20panel%20at%20top%20is%20shown%20on%20the%20floor%20against%20a%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6041487bb46d720018b04f74%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Feeder-Robot%20is%20the%20most%20convenient%20pet%20feeder%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E32%20cups%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20source%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAC%20power%20source%20or%20backup%20battery%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWiFi-enabled%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EControl%20panel%20on%20device%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompatible%20foods%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Dry%20and%20semi-moist%20kibble%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EMeals%20per%20day%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Up%20to%204%20or%20free%20feed%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDimensions%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E13%20inches%20wide%2C%2015%20inches%20high%2C%2012.5%20deep%3B%20footprint%20is%209%20inches%20wide%2C%2011.25%20deep%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWarranty%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E90-day%20money-back%20guarantee%2C%2018-month%20warranty%2C%20extended%203-year%20warranty%20(%2430)%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPros%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWiFi-enabled%2C%20large%20capacity%2C%20programmable%20via%20control%20panel%20or%20app%2C%20money-back%20guarantee%2C%20warranty%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECons%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ELess%20than%2024%20hours%20of%20backup%20battery%20life%2C%20WiFi%20and%20power%20outages%20prevent%20data%20tracking%20via%20app%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20large-capacity%20Feeder-Robot%20ranked%20highest%20in%20ease%20of%20use%20and%20functionality%20among%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders.%20It%20can%20be%20programmed%20to%20dispense%20scheduled%20feedings%20or%20keep%20the%20dish%20full%20at%20all%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20device%20required%20little%20assembly%20and%20was%20easy%20to%20connect%20to%20WiFi.%20With%20the%20built-in%20control%20panel%2C%20you%20can%20program%20meals%20and%20portion%20sizes%20and%20send%20a%20snack.%20The%20same%20functions%20can%20be%20controlled%20via%20the%20app%2C%20which%20also%20lets%20you%20change%20the%20feeding%20schedule%20for%20different%20days%20of%20the%20week%20and%20track%20how%20much%20your%20pet%20eats%20on%20average%20per%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20cats%20ate%20from%20the%20Feeder-Robot%20without%20any%20trouble%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20jam%20during%20testing.%20Because%20the%20dish%20is%20wide%20and%20shallow%2C%20there's%20no%20risk%20of%20whisker%20fatigue.%20The%20mechanical%20whir%20of%20the%20hopper%20and%20cascade%20of%20kibble%20that%20followed%20were%20audible%20from%20other%20rooms%20but%20weren't%20so%20loud%20that%20they%20startled%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20WiFi%20goes%20out%2C%20the%20feeder%20continues%20to%20dispense%20food%2C%20but%20the%20app%20stops%20tracking%20the%20meals%20and%20snacks%20dispensed.%20Unfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20receive%20a%20push%20notification%20when%20the%20connection%20was%20lost.%20I%20had%20to%20open%20the%20app%20or%20look%20at%20the%20feeder's%20control%20panel%20to%20see%20if%20it%20was%20offline.%20When%20I%20turned%20the%20WiFi%20back%20on%2C%20the%20feeder%20reconnected%20to%20the%20internet%20within%20seconds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20backup%20battery%20steps%20in%20during%20power%20outages.%20In%20my%20test%2C%20the%20battery%20lasted%2021.5%20hours%20instead%20of%20the%20advertised%2024%20hours.%20The%20app%20also%20did%20not%20notify%20me%20when%20the%20power%20went%20out%2C%20so%20this%20feeder%20isn't%20a%20