sizes%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20notify%20you%20when%20the%20food%20level%20is%20low%20or%20the%20machine%20is%20offline%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20control%20panel%20on%20the%20feeder%20that%20can%20be%20used%20if%20the%20WiFi%20connection%20is%20lost%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20track%20how%20often%20and%20how%20much%20your%20cat%20eats%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20ability%20to%20send%20a%20snack%20on%20demand%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20wide%2C%20shallow%20food%20dish%20that%20slopes%20toward%20the%20cat%20for%20easy%20access%20and%20the%20prevention%20of%20whisker%20fatigue%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20easy-to-remove%20washable%20food%20dish%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%3Cp%3EWe%20tested%20each%20of%20the%20seven%20pet%20feeders%20in%20this%20guide%20for%20at%20least%20three%20weeks.%20In%20addition%20to%20monitoring%20the%20reliability%20of%20each%20device%2C%20we%20also%20considered%20the%20following%20when%20selecting%20the%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20assembly%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20feeders%20arrived%20almost%20fully%20assembled%2C%20while%20others%20required%20some%20effort%20to%20put%20together.%20I%20assessed%20how%20quickly%20and%20easily%20I%20could%20set%20up%20each%20feeder%2C%20including%20whether%20I%20had%20to%20purchase%20batteries.%20For%20the%20smart-enabled%20devices%2C%20I%20determined%20how%20quickly%20and%20easily%20the%20feeder%20connected%20to%20WiFi%20and%20its%20mobile%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20programming%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20control%20panels%20on%20each%20device%20varied%20significantly.%20I%20considered%20how%20complicated%20they%20were%20to%20use%20by%20programming%20each%20to%20dispense%20three%20meals%20daily.%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20whether%20the%20size%20of%20a%20meal%20could%20be%20adjusted%20from%20feeding%20to%20feeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECapacity%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Although%20the%20automatic%20feeders%20we%20tested%20have%20different%20functions%2C%20I%20measured%20how%20much%20food%20each%20machine%20could%20hold.%20For%20the%20large-capacity%20feeders%2C%20I%20also%20determined%20whether%20the%20machine%20or%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20smart%20feeders%2C%20the%20app%20notified%20me%20when%20the%20food%20was%20running%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENoise%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20the%20machine%20dispensed%20a%20meal%2C%20I%20evaluated%20whether%20just%20the%20cats%20could%20hear%20it%20or%20if%20the%20humans%20could%2C%20too.%20Some%20feeders%20were%20louder%20than%20others%2C%20and%20some%20even%20triggered%20a%20startle%20response%20in%20the%20cats.%20I%20also%20considered%20whether%20a%20feeder%20could%20be%20programmed%20to%20play%20a%20personalized%20voice%20recording%20to%20call%20my%20cats%20to%20their%20dinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20and%20WiFi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20it's%20essential%20that%20a%20feeder%20reliably%20dispenses%20meals%20even%20when%20you're%20away%20from%20home%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20the%20power%20supply%20for%20each.%20While%20some%20feeders%20run%20solely%20on%20batteries%2C%20others%20rely%20on%20an%20outlet%20and%20have%20a%20limited%20backup%20battery%2C%20if%20any.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20know%20whether%20the%20smart%20feeders%20would%20continue%20to%20work%20if%20the%20WiFi%20went%20down%20and%20how%20long%20it%20took%20a%20feeder%20to%20come%20back%20online.%20I%20tested%20this%20by%20turning%20off%20the%20WiFi%20several%20times%20for%20anywhere%20from%205%20minutes%20to%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECat%20accessibility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20cat%20needs%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20eating%20from%20an%20automatic%20feeder%20in%20order%20for%20it%20to%20do%20its%20job.%20I%20monitored%20my%20two%20cats%20to%20see%20how%20easily%20they%20could%20access%20food%20and%20whether%20the%20machine%20or%20its%20dispensing%20nozzle%20got%20in%20the%20way.%20I%20also%20considered%20the%20size%20and%20shape%20of%20each%20dish%2C%20favoring%20those%20that%20were%20wide%20and%20shallow%20enough%20to%20prevent%20whisker%20fatigue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMobile%20app%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20mobile%20app%20for%20an%20automatic%20feeder%20should%20be%20straightforward%20to%20use%20for%20even%20the%20least%20technologically%20savvy.%20I%20played%20around%20in%20the%20apps%20of%20each%20smart%20feeder%20to%20determine%20how%20challenging%20it%20was%20to%20schedule%20meals%2C%20send%20a%20snack%2C%20and%20track%20my%20cats'%20eating%20habits.%20Because%20an%20app%20will%20not%20connect%20to%20the%20smart%20feeder%20when%20the%20WiFi%20is%20out%2C%20I%20also%20looked%20at%20whether%20a%20feeder%20had%20a%20control%20panel%20that%20could%20be%20set%20and%20adjusted%20without%20internet%20access.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20cleaning%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20testing%20the%20machines%2C%20I%20thoroughly%20cleaned%20each%20one%2C%20noting%20which%20had%20parts%20that%20could%20be%20thrown%20in%20the%20dishwasher%20and%20which%20had%20to%20be%20washed%20by%20hand%20or%20wiped%20down%20with%20a%20moist%20cloth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESmart%20automatic%20feeders%20vs.%20dumb%20automatic%20feeders%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Feeder%20Robot%20microchip%20feeder%20with%20control%20panel%20beside%20an%20app%20screenshot%20showing%20a%20cat's%20average%20daily%20food%20intake.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F633db4d6df105f00184f725b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Feeder-Robot%20has%20a%20companion%20app%20that%20tells%20you%20how%20often%20and%20how%20much%20your%20cat%20eats.%3Cp%3EShoshi%20Parks%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDumb%20feeders%20allow%20you%20to%20program%20the%20frequency%20and%20size%20of%20meals%20on%20a%20control%20panel%20embedded%20in%20the%20machine.%20Smart%20feeders%20are%20relatively%20new%20to%20the%20automatic%20feeder%20game.%20They%20are%20WiFi-enabled%20devices%20that%20pair%20with%20a%20mobile%20app%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20mealtime%2C%20portion%20size%2C%20and%20feeding%20frequency%20remotely.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20like%20the%20Surefeed%20Connect%20Microchip%20Feeder%2C%20smart%20auto-feeders%20also%20measure%20how%20often%20and%20how%20much%20a%20pet%20consumes%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20dumb%20feeders%20we%20tested%20for%20this%20guide%20were%20either%20100%25%20battery-operated%20or%20had%20the%20option%20to%20operate%20the%20machine%20with%20either%20batteries%20or%20a%20power%20cord.%20The%20three%20smart%20feeders%20we%20tested%20also%20had%20both%20battery%20and%20power%20cord%20options.%20However%2C%20smart%20feeders%20don't%20just%20need%20electricity%3B%20they%20also%20need%20WiFi%2C%20which%20presents%20a%20problem%20when%20one%20or%20both%20go%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20found%20the%20smart%20feeders%20we%20tested%20got%20back%20online%20quickly%20after%20power%20outages%20of%20different%20lengths.%20During%20outages%2C%20tracking%20data%20in%20the%20app%20was%20disrupted%2C%20but%20it%20resumed%20without%20a%20hitch%20when%20the%20connection%20returned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20power%20or%20WiFi%20outages%20are%20unlikely%20to%20cause%20significant%20problems.%20Your%20cat%20may%20be%20miffed%20if%20they%20miss%20a%20meal%2C%20but%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20they%20claim%20otherwise%2C%20they'll%20be%20just%20fine.%20However%2C%20if%20you%20happen%20to%20be%20out%20of%20town%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20an%20extended%20power%20outage%20or%20a%20machine%20that%20fails%20to%20come%20back%20online%20following%20a%20shorter%20outage%20could%20have%20serious%20consequences.%20The%20battery%20on%20the%20Feeder-Robot%20lasted%20only%2021.5%20hours%20before%20the%20machine%20shut%20down.%20Worse%20yet%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20smart%20feeder%2C%20even%20if%20you've%20turned%20on%20notifications%2C%20you%20may%20not%20know%20something%20is%20wrong%20unless%20you%20enter%20the%20app.%20The%20Feeder-Robot%20failed%20to%20notify%20me%20when%20the%20WiFi%20or%20power%20went%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20light%20of%20these%20issues%2C%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20use%20your%20automatic%20feeder%20frequently%20during%20short%20overnight%20trips%2C%20you%20may%20be%20better%20off%20choosing%20one%20that%20operates%20solely%20on%20batteries%20to%20avoid%20the%20potential%20snafu%20power%20outages%20may%20present.%20Otherwise%2C%20be%20sure%20to%20have%20a%20trusted%20human%20ready%20to%20take%20over%20feeding%20if%20duty%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-feeder%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719001712000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6675c19c65f501a8818137f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-feeder%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20best%20automatic%20cat%20feeders%20reliably%20dispense%20wet%20food%2C%20kibble%2C%20or%20both.%20Our%20top%20picks%20include%20a%20camera%20feeder%20and%20one%20that%20keeps%20canned%20food%20cold.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Janelle%20Leeson%2CJulie%20Liu%2C%20DVM)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-cat-feeder%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK's%20richest%20family%20convicted%20of%20exploiting%20servants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719001510000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3f8c%2Flive%2F288767b0-2fea-11ef-a044-9d4367d5b599.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc3ggl6pe52eo%230%22%2C%2