%20because%20I%20notoriously%20hate%20wired%20styles%2C%20I've%20carved%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20niche%20as%20an%20expert%20in%20wireless%20bras.%20I've%20tried%20styles%20from%20almost%20every%20brand%20you%20could%20think%20of%2C%20so%20whenever%20a%20new%20company%20makes%20the%20claim%20that%20their%20wireless%20bras%20are%20%26quot%3Btruly%20unique%2C%26quot%3B%20you%20can%20imagine%20me%20over%20here%20twiddling%20my%20thumbs%20%E2%80%94%20always%20interested%20in%20trying%20them%20out%20and%20often%20disappointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20after%20all%20these%20years%2C%20I%20think%20I've%20found%20the%20brand%20making%20the%20world's%20best%20wireless%20bras%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20brand%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fevelynbobbie.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEvelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEvelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie's%20wireless%20bras%20are%20legitimately%20the%20most%20comfortable%20I've%20ever%20worn.%20They're%20supportive%2C%20structured%2C%20not%20too%20constrictive%2C%20and%20they%20actively%20take%20weight%20off%20my%20shoulders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20image%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20black%20bra%20and%20a%20close%20up%20shot%20of%20the%20bra%20strap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66746c56886e840164be7560%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20seamless%20bras%20have%20a%20smoothing%20back%20and%20disappear%20under%20clothes%2C%20making%20them%20perfect%20for%20wearing%20under%20a%20T-shirt.%20I%20kept%20the%20thin%20foam%20pad%20in%20the%20bra%20because%20I%20like%20the%20shaping%20effect%2C%20but%20you%20can%20remove%20it%20if%20you%20prefer.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20introduction%20to%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%20was%20when%20the%20brand%20sent%20me