ntinued%20testing%20to%20find%20out%20what%20made%20these%20bras%20so%20good%2C%20and%20it%20turns%20out%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20science%20behind%20why%20they're%20so%20comfortable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20bras%20are%20designed%20with%20a%20patented%20material%20technology%20that%20supports%20the%20chest%20from%20underneath%20and%20takes%20weight%20off%20the%20shoulders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20original%20photograph%20of%20a%20finger%20pointing%20at%20the%20interior%20cup%20of%20an%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%20wireless%20bra%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66699f50764df1611258d340%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20can%20see%20where%20I'm%20pointing%20how%20the%20material%20on%20the%20side%20and%20bottom%20of%20the%20cup%20is%20much%20more%20structured%20than%20the%20material%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20cup.%20This%20helps%20to%20hold%20your%20breast%20in%20place%20so%20it%20doesn't%20pancake%20out%20to%20the%20side%2C%20and%20it%20takes%20some%20of%20the%20weight%20off%20your%20shoulders%20by%20supporting%20the%20breast%20from%20below.%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%20currently%20only%20makes%20wireless%20bras%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20they%20are%20100%25%20focused%20on%20nailing%20this%20particular%20style.%20The%20founder%2C%20Bree%20McKeen%2C%20holds%20several%20patents%20for%20the%20supportive%20technology%20called%20%26quot%3BEB%20Core%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20built%20into%20each%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EB%20Core%20support%20structure%20for%20each%20breast%20is%20a%20low-stretch%20material%20that's%20built%20into%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20cups%20and%20band%2C%20which%20takes%20the%20weight%20off%20of%20your%20shoulders%20and%20distributes%20it%20more%20evenly.%20Supporting%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20breast%20from%20below%20is%20exactly%20what%20wired%20bras%20attempt%20to%20do%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20much%20harder%20feat%20to%20achieve%20in%20a%20wireless%20style.%20The%20specially%20bonded%20material%20that%20runs%20through%20the%20underside%20of%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie's%20molded%20cups%20is%20really%20where%20the%20magic%20happens.%20Because%20it%20doesn't%20have%20as%20much%20stretch%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20material%2C%20it%20holds%20the%20breast's%20weight%20and%20helps%20shape%20it%20so%20there's%20no%20pancaking%20on%20the%20side.%20That%20extra%20support%20is%20also%20what%20keeps%20the%20band%20from%20stretching%20out%20so%20the%20bra%20can%20maintain%20its%20shape%20for%20longer%20than%20a%20basic%20molded%20cup%20would%20(hence%20no%20uniboobs%20or%20sagging%20after%20a%20few%20weeks%20of%20wear).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20straps%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20are%20adjustable%20%E2%80%94%20also%20utilize%20the%20same%20bonded%20structure%20technology%20%26quot%3Bto%20ensure%20that%20the%20weight%20of%20your%20bust%20sits%20perfectly%20on%20your%20shoulder-clavicle%20joint%2C%20not%20over%20the%20delicate%20trapezius%20muscle%2C%26quot%3B%20which%2C%20according%20to%20their%20website%20(and%20my%20extensive%20testing)%2C%20prevents%20the%20kind%20of%20painful%20indentations%20that%20other%20bra%20straps%20can%20cause.%20After%20wearing%20each%20style%20and%20comparing%20it%20to%20my%20regular%20wireless%20bras%2C%20which%20have%20all%20caused%20indents%20on%20my%20shoulders%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20back%20the%20brand's%20claims%20about%20weight%20distribution%20and%20shoulder%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EEvelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie's%20bras%20use%20alpha%20sizing%20and%20come%20in%20a%20range%20from%20XS%20to%203XL.%20I%20was%20skeptical%20that%20this%20sizing%20scheme%20would%20actually%20work%2C%20but%20it%20did.%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20some%20miracle%2C%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%20has%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20make%20alpha%20sizing%20work%20rather%20than%20offering%20every%20bra%20in%20an%20exact%20band%20and%20cup%20size.%20As%20a%2036DDD%2C%20the%20brand's%20sizing%20chart%20put%20me%20at%20a%20size%20large%20for%20each%20style%20I%20tried.%20I%20thought%20there%20was%20no%20way%20it%20would%20fit%20well%2C%20but%20I%20was%20instantly%20proven%20wrong%2C%20style%20after%20style.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sizing%20options%20range%20from%20XS%20to%20a%20size-inclusive%203XL%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20more%20inclusive%20bra%20brands%20out%20there.%20And%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20bras%20that%20come%20in%20a%20diverse%20size%20range.%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie's%20underwear%20comes%20in%20two%20sizes%20with%20one%20fitting%20a%200-14%20and%20the%20other%20a%2016-24%20%E2%80%94%20so%20its%20efforts%20to%20serve%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20bodies%20seem%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20brand's%20DNA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20%2498%20each%2C%20these%20bras%20are%20not%20cheap%2C%20but%20they%20are%20beyond%20worth%20it.%20The%20comfort%20is%20unparalleled%20and%2C%20in%20my%20many%20years%20of%20testing%20wireless%20bras%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20hesitate%20to%20call%20these%20the%20best%20wireless%20bras%20ever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fevelynbobbie.com%2Fcollections%2Fthe-wireless-bras%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShop%20all%20wireless%20bras%20from%20Evelyn%20%26amp%3B%20Bobbie%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fevelyn-and-bobbie-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719000812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66699f07e079049018180854%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fevelyn-and-bobbie-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20have%20DDD%20cups%2