0and%20another%20leg%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-the-eras-tour-taylorgating-experience-without-ticket-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift's%20Eras%20Tour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Europe%20will%20likely%20be%20a%20popular%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20exciting%20as%20traveling%20is%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20stressful.%20Long%20flights%2C%20jet%20lag%2C%20and%20packed%20itineraries%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20prioritize%20physical%20and%20mental%20fitness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20four-time%20Olympic%20medalist%20and%20British%20diving%20legend%20Tom%20Daley%20through%20his%20partnership%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetrainline.com%2Fen-us%2Fvia%2Feurope%2Ftom-daleys-summer-sports-tour-of-europe%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrainline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20European%20train%20booking%20app%2C%20to%20learn%20his%20top%20tips%20for%20staying%20fit%20while%20traveling%20this%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20you're%20headed%20to%20Paris%20like%20Daley%2C%20the%20Eras%20Tour%2C%20or%20any%20other%20corner%20of%20the%20world%2C%20here%20are%20his%20five%20recommendations%20to%20maintain%20your%20physical%20and%20mental%20health%20while%20on%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20most%20important%20thing%20to%20remember%20when%20traveling%20is%20your%20routine%2C%20according%20to%20Daley.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tom%20Daley%20attends%20the%20GQ%20Men%20Of%20The%20Year%20Awards%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66744c282efa138e03312751%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222834%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Daley%20attends%20the%20GQ%20Men%20Of%20The%20Year%20Awards%202023.%3Cp%3EMike%20Marsland%2FContributor%2FWireImage%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDaley%2C%2030%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20when%20traveling%20is%20to%20try%20to%20maintain%20some%20kind%20of%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20diving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teamgb.com%2Fathlete%2Ftom-daley%2F3y6lj3NwM4u2dORkh8DkXo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eat%20age%207%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20made%20his%20Olympic%20debut%20in%202008%20at%20just%2014%20%E2%80%94%20understandably%2C%20Daley%20said%20his%20body%20has%20changed%20since%20then%2C%20impacting%20how%20he%20can%20and%20can't%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20traveling%20when%20you're%2010%20to%2015%20years%20old%2C%20you%20don't%20really%20have%20many%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20as%20soon%20as%20you%20start%20getting%20a%20little%20bit%20older%2C%20and%20as%20I've%20been%20more%20of%20an%20athlete%20now%20for%2023%20years%2C%20I%20just%20have%20to%20start%20thinking%20about%20how%20can%20I%20look%20after%20myself%20best%20when%20I'm%20traveling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20routine%20is%20also%20an%20important%20part%20of%20how%20he%20stays%20disciplined%20while%20training%20and%20focused%20during%20competitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20one%20way%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20motivated%20and%20determined%20and%20committed%20to%20what%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20a%20sense%20of%20routine.%20Being%20able%20to%20stick%20to%20the%20routine%2C%20being%20able%20to%20know%20what%20you're%20going%20to%20be%20doing%2C%20when%2C%20it's%20all%20about%20the%20consistency%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20consistently%20stick%20to%20your%20routine%2C%20then%20you'll%20eventually%20get%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%20you%20normally%20like%20to%20go%20for%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20mornings%2C%20plan%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20on%20vacation%3B%20this%20will%20give%20you%20something%20familiar%20to%20do%20while%20you're%20away%20from%20home%20and%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20c