eceived%20two%20price%20target%20increases%20on%20Friday%20from%20CFRA%20and%20Bernstein.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20research%20firms%20both%20raised%20their%20Apple%20price%20target%20to%20%24240%2C%20representing%20potential%20upside%20of%2014%25.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple's%20WWDC%20event%20last%20week%20showcased%20its%20new%20AI%20technologies%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20impress%20Wall%20Street.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Faapl-stock%3FmiRedirects%3D1%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20could%20surge%20another%2014%25%20as%20it%20becomes%20the%20leader%20in%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20according%20to%20two%20Wall%20Street%20research%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20CFRA%20and%20Bernstein%20increased%20their%20Apple%20price%20target%20to%20%24240%20per%20share%20on%20Friday.%20That's%20after%20Apple%20stock%20experienced%20a%2027%25%20rally%20since%20its%20late-April%20low%20of%20about%20%24165%20per%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CFRA%20analyst%20Angelo%20Zino%2C%20who%20previously%20had%20a%20%24210%20price%20target%2C%20Apple%20is%20poised%20to%20turn%20the%20iPhone%20into%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20personal%20assistant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20showed%20off%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-stock-wwdc-ai-announcements-siri-openai-wall-street-outlook-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20%26quot%3BApple%20Intelligence%26quot%3B%20product%20offering%20at%20WWDC%20last%20week%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20turbocharges%20Siri%20into%20a%20smart%20digital%20assistant%20that%20is%20more%20conversational%20than%20today's%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZino%20said%20Wall%20Street%20analysts%20are%20underestimating%20Apple's%20iPhone%2016%20unit%20sales%2C%20of%20which%20he%20expects%20unit%20growth%20of%203%25%20to%205%25%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20company%20has%20leverage%20to%20raise%20iPhone%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20expect%20Apple%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20to%20help%20support%20incremental%20consumer%20upgrades%2C%20driven%20by%20loyalists%20and%20an%20aging%20installed%20base%2C%20with%20AI%20being%20more%20evolutionary%20than%20cyclical%20that%20will%20aid%20multiple%20years%20of%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Zino%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20analyst%20Toni%20Sacconaghi%20also%20sees%20considerable%20upside%20ahead%20for%20Apple%20Stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESacconaghi%20argued%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-stock-wwdc-ai-announcements-siri-openai-wall-street-outlook-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple's%20WWDC%20keynote%20presentation%3C%2Fa%3E%20turned%20the%20company%20into%20an%20AI%20leader%2C%20with%20its%20ability%20to%20bring%20AI%20to%20the%20masses%20via%20its%20more%20than%20one%20billion%20installed%20base%20of%20iPhone%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20can%20bring%20AI%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20with%20increasing%2C%20everyday%20utility%2C%26quot%3B%20Sacconaghi%20said.%20%26quot%3BApple%20is%20reportedly%20not%20paying%20ChatGPT%2C%20highlighting%20the%20power%20that%20it%20holds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20is%20offering%20an%20integration%20of%20ChatGPT%20in%20its%20upcoming%20AI%20offering%2C%20set%20to%20be%20released%20with%20the%20iPhone%2016%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Apple's%20massive%20installed%20base%20means%20it%20has%20a%20big%20opportunity%20ahead%20to%20monetize%20AI%20features%2C%20according%20to%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20AI%20features%20driving%20a%20more%20robust%20upgrade%20cycle%20for%20the%20iPhone%2C%20Apple%20could%20collect%20advertising%20revenues%20through%20AI%20search%20queries%2C%20as%20well%20as%20higher%20app%20store%20revenues%20if%20more%20AI-focused%20apps%20are%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20the%20company%20could%20leverage%20Apple%20Intelligence%20%26quot%3Bto%20serve%20as%20a%20channel%20intermediary%20to%20third%20party%20apps%2C%20with%20Apple%20capturing%20a%20commission%20on%20commerce%20or%20a%20promotion%20fee%2C%26quot%3B%20Sacconaghi%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein%20bases%20its%20%24240%20price%20target%20on%20fiscal%20year%202025%20earnings%20per%20share%20of%20%248.00%20and%20a%20historically%20high%20multiple%20of%2030x%20earnings.%20Sacconaghi%20previously%20had%20a%20%24195%20price%20target%20for%20Apple%20stock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-stock-price-prediction-240-price-target-ai-leadership-iphone-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718994808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6675b27340cf2af6e4f4ac9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-stock-price-prediction-240-price-target-ai-leadership-iphone-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20poised%20to%20turn%20the%20iPhone%20into%20%26quot%3Bthe%20ultimate%20personal%20assistant%26quot%3B%20with%20its%20upcoming%20release%20of%20a%20revamped%20Siri%2C%20CFRA%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A134%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fapple-stock-price-prediction-240-price-target-ai-leadership-iphone-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Swiss%20court%20jails%204%20Hinduja%20family%20members%20for%20exploiting%20domestic%20staff%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718994711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-04%2F28%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1714322481-0142.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busines