wn%20as%20the%20cultural%20capital%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20is%20not%20fueled%20by%20the%20Opposition%20but%20by%20the%20ruling%20party%20itself%2C%20the%20electricity%20department%20employees%20said.%20All%20the%20employees%20have%20rallied%20in%20protest%2C%20displaying%20posters%20and%20decrying%20the%20actions%20taken%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20centres%20around%20allegations%20that%20a%20BJP%20councillor%20built%20an%20illegal%20colony%20and%20took%20an%20illegal%20electricity%20connection.%20When%20legal%20action%20was%20initiated%2C%20the%20councillor%20allegedly%20responded%20with%20violence%20to%20exert%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFalse%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20us.%20We%20will%20go%20on%20strike%20if%20necessary.%20The%20recovery%20of%20Rs%2018-20%20lakh%20was%20made%20against%20the%20councillor.%20When%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20they%20created%20a%20ruckus%2C%20and%20BJP%20leaders%20Atul%20Dani%20and%20Pushpendra%20resorted%20to%20vandalism%20without%20attempting%20to%20resolve%20the%20issue%20through%20dialogue%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20electricity%20department%20employee%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMobile%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20show%20BJP%20councillor%20Atul%20Dani%20entering%20a%20meeting%20on%20June%2019%2C%20and%20shouting%20at%20the%20department%20employees%2C%20which%20raised%20tension.%20Subsequently%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20accused%20the%20electricity%20department%20officials%20of%20misconduct%2C%20citing%20unnecessary%20power%20cuts%20and%20exploitation%20through%20smart%20meters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20our%20mandal%20president%20and%20councillor%20faced%20misbehaviour%20with.%20Complaints%20were%20filed%2C%20and%20casteist%20remarks%20were%20made.%20It's%20my%20responsibility%20to%20address%20these%20issues.%20If%20anyone%20tries%20to%20undermine%20the%20government's%20work%2C%20we%20will%20face%20it%20courageously%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20MLA%20Abhilash%20Pandey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20worsened%20when%20three%20BJP%20MLAs%20and%2015%20councillors%20blocked%20the%20road%20for%20five%20hours%2C%20staging%20a%20dharna.%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20police%20filed%20cases%20against%2012%20employees%20and%20officers%20of%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Vidyut%20Mandal%20under%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20police%20may%20have%20overlooked%20the%20fact%20two%20of%20the%20officers%20who%20were%20allegedly%20assaulted%20are%20from%20the%20SC%2FST%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20FIR%20(first%20information%20report)%20has%20been%20filed%20based%20on%20the%20application%20received.%20The%20police%20will%20take%20action%20after%20an%20impartial%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20SP%20Samar%20Verma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20protests%20continue%2C%20the%20electricity%20department%20employees%20alleged%20politically%20motivated%20actions%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718993340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fc8j14ghg_jabalpur-protest_625x300_21_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpower-department-staff-bjp-leaders-face-off-in-madhya-pradeshs-jabalpur-over-alleged-dues-5941494%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20dramatic%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20BJP%20leaders%20have%20clashed%20with%20officers%20from%20the%20electricity%20department%20in%20Jabalpur%20over%20allegations%20of%20electricity%20theft%2C%20leading%20to%20vandalism%20in%20the%20department's%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpower-department-staff-bjp-leaders-face-off-in-madhya-pradeshs-jabalpur-over-alleged-dues-5941494%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpower-depart