hts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20place%20where%20you%20can%20run%20with%20your%20kids%20and%20experience%20nature%20in%20full%20glory.%20We%20have%20created%20an%20escape%20from%20city%20life%20and%20its%20rat-race%20so%20you%20can%20experience%20nature%20in%20its%20raw%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aseem%2C%20the%20co-founder%20of%20the%20homestay%2C%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20homestay%20is%20not%20only%20made%20with%20zero-cement%20and%20local%20wood%20but%20also%20has%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest%20and%20is%20pet-friendly.%20So%2C%20whether%20you%20are%20having%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20or%20a%20boiled%20egg%2C%20everything%20is%20grown%20on%20the%20property.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20how%20did%20this%20couple%20with%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332749%2Fex-banker-sunando-sen-built-tanhau-sustainable-himalayan-homestay-corbett-restore-wildlife%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20life%20in%20a%20metropolitan%20city%20switch%20to%20farm%20living%3F%20%3C%2Fa%3EHere%20is%20their%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20family%20affair%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitting%20across%20in%20their%20homestay%E2%80%99s%20lounge%2C%20Aseem%2C%20Neetu%2C%20and%20their%20daughter%20eagerly%20share%20the%20story%20of%20their%20life%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20lived%20in%20Gurgaon%20on%20the%20ninth%20floor%20of%20an%20apartment%20building%20and%20felt%20increasingly%20disconnected%20from%20nature.%20Both%20of%20us%20wanted%20to%20escape%20the%20rat-race%20and%20provide%20our%20daughter%20with%20a%20better%20life.%20Every%20day%2C%20we%20would%20hear%20news%20about%20food%20adulteration%20which%20deeply%20concerned%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20general%20manager%20at%20ITC%2C%20and%20Neetu%2C%20who%20worked%20at%20MakeMyTrip%2C%20were%20already%20familiar%20with%20the%20hotel%20industry.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20community%20and%20a%20home%20where%20people%20could%20come%20to%20take%20a%20break%20from%20city%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20was%20already%20in%20love%20with%20the%20mountains%20and%20which%20place%20was%20better%20than%20%E2%80%98The%20Queen%20Of%20Hills%E2%80%99%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20to%20look%20for%20places%20before%20deciding%20to%20move.%20One%20thing%20that%20we%20noticed%20was%20that%20the%20hill%20station%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20big%20buildings%20but%20we%20did%20not%20want%20that.%20We%20wanted%20to%20give%20a%20break%20to%20people%20from%20the%20hustle%20and%20bustle%20of%20cities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aseem%20and%20Neetu%20Varma%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-2-1718977526-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353894%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAseem%20and%20Neetu%20Varma%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20looking%20for%20some%20time%2C%20the%20couple%20finally%20found%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346785%2Fraison-detre-homestay-in-kullu-manali-near-beas-river-natural-spring-nitin-shalini-beri-sustainable%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20their%20dream%20place.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20know%20how%20as%20a%20kid%20you%20would%20draw%20two%20big%20mountains%2C%20a%20river%20and%20a%20home%20on%20the%20side%3F%C2%A0%20That%20is%20exactly%20what%20the%20place%20looked%20like.%20It%20was%20near%20Kempty%20Falls%20and%20had%20a%20river%20passing%20through%20just%20below.%20There%20was%20a%2050-year-old%20broken%20down%20structure%20which%20we%20used%20as%20a%20base%20for%20our%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Neetu.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20bought%20the%20property%20in%202015%20and%20Neetu%20quit%20her%20job.%20A%20year%20later%2C%20Aseem%20followed%20suit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20were%20constructing%20the%20homestay%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20locals%20told%20us%20that%20no%20one%20would%20come%20to%20the%20place%20as%20it%20is%20not%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20city.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20important%20for%20us%20to%20create%20an%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20a%20self-sustaining%20place%20rather%20than%20a%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20opened%20our%20doors%20to%20guests%20in%202017.%20We%20currently%20have%207%20rooms%20and%20have%20hosted%20over%2010%2C000%20guests%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20self-sustaining%20home%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20lay%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Brigadiar%E2%80%99s%20Cottage%20was%20sustainability.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20what%20we%20use%20to%20make%20our%20home%20and%20what%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20%E2%80%94%20we%20wanted%20it%20all%20to%20be%20as%20eco-friendly%20as%20we%20could.%20We%20did%20not%20use%20any%20cement%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house.%20We%20used%20only%20locally-sourced%20materials%20and%20hired%20local%20artists%20to%20do%20the%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAseem%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20not%20only%20provided%20jobs%20for%20the%20locals%20but%20also%20reduced%20the%20carbon%20footprint%20we%20would%20have%20created.%20Although%20we%20cannot%20use%20it%20in%20the%20winters%2C%20we%20also%20have%20solar%20power%20in%20the%20homestay%2C%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20has%20also%20planted%20300%20trees%20ever%20since%20they%20purchased%20the%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neetu%20and%20Aseem%20have%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-3-1718977632-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353896%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeetu%20and%20Aseem%20have%20a%20poultry%20farm%2C%20a%20dairy%20farm%2C%20an%20apiary%2C%20and%20an%20organic%20food%20forest.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20it%2C%20Neetu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20not%20just%20to%20create%20an%20escape%20for%20adults%20but%20also%20a%20space%20for%20the%20kids%20to%20explore%20nature.%20Today%E2%80%99s%20kids%20are%20drinking%20milk%20out%20of%20cartons%20and%20eating%20chicken%20from%20KFC.%20The%20idea%20was%20to%20create%20an%20organic%20space%2C%20an%20organic%20lifestyle%20for%20not%20only%20our%20daughter%20but%20for%20all%20the%20kids%20we%20could%20offer%20it%20to.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEverything%20that%20we%20serve%20to%20the%20guests%20comes%20from%20our%20farms.%20We%20even%20make%20our%20own%20oil%20from%20walnuts%2C%20groundnuts%20and%20mustard%20seeds.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeetu%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20produce%20our%20own%20honey%20with%2023%20bee%20boxes.%20We%20grow%20turmeric%20and%20chia%20seeds%20and%20have%20our%20own%20dairy%20for%20milk.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20maintain%20a%20small%20poultry%20farm%20with%20around%2030%20chickens%20for%20eggs.%20Vegetables%20are%20sourced%20from%20local%20farms%20as%20well.%20Essentially%2C%20everything%20we%20consume%20here%20is%20either%20grown%20or%20raised%20by%20us%20or%20sourced%20from%20the%20organic%20farms%20nearby.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302308%2Fbengaluru-couple-grows-organic-food-forest-using-permaculture-build-sustainable-mud-house%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealso%20follows%20a%20no-waste%20policy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20try%20to%20use%20everything%20that%20we%20procure.%20All%20the%20food%20waste%20becomes%20fodder%20for%20our%20livestock.%20All%20the%20cow%20dung%20is%20converted%20and%20made%20into%20organic%20incense%20sticks%20to%20be%20used%20in%20the%20homestay%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Aseem%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC54wullSoM3%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20The%20Brigadiers%20Cottage%2C%20Mussoorie.%20(%40brigadierscottagemussoorie)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20spend%20time%20at%20the%20homestay%3F%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20guests%20come%20to%20stay%20with%20us%2C%20they%20usually%20book%20a%20three-night%20stay.%20On%20the%20first%20day%2C%20they%20arrive%20at%20the%20cottage%20by%20the%20afternoon%2C%20usually%20post-lunch%2C%20after%20a%20long%20drive%20from%20places%20like%20Delhi%20or%20Mumbai.%20We%20encourage%20them%20to%20settle%20down%20and%20relax%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aseem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20common%20dining%20area%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20the%20dining%20room%20or%20the%20terrace%2C%20then%20becomes%20a%20gathering%20spot%20in%20the%20evening.%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20winter%2C%20we%20have%20bonfires%20to%20enhance%20the%20cosy%20atmosphere.%20On%20the%20second%20day%2C%20we%20recommend%20exploring%20the%20local%20sights%20like%20Landour%20and%20the%20Mall%20Road.%20Guests%20often%20spend%20the%20day%20sightseeing%20and%20enjoying%20the%20local%20attractions.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20third%20day%2C%20we%20ask%20the%20guests%20to%20visit%20the%20Benog%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary.%20We%20have%20a%20local%20guide%20who%20is%20very%20knowledgeable%20about%20herbs%20and%20the%20area.%20He%20takes%20the%20guests%20on%20a%20trail%20through%20the%20jungle%20to%20the%20waterfalls.%20Depending%20on%20their%20preference%2C%20the%20trail%20can%20be%20a%20short%20one-hour%20walk%20or%20a%20longer%20four-hour%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20is%20also%20a%20bird%20sanctuary%2C%20making%20it%20a%20paradise%20for%20bird%20watchers.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20guests%20have%20spotted%20rare%20birds%20such%20as%20the%20blue-throated%20barbet%2C%20plum-headed%20parakeet%2C%20and%20Himalayan%20bulbul%20from%20our%20cottage%2C%20and%20even%20more%20when%20they%20go%20on%20the%20trails.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20morning%20hike%20and%20bird%20watching%2C%20guests%20come%20back%20for%20breakfast%20and%20then%20head%20down%20to%20the%20Yamuna%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbrigadiers-cottage-4-1718977690.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cottage%20offers%20scenic%20views%20of%20the%20hills.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024