d%20his%20wife%20Neetu%20left%20their%20flourishing%20careers%20to%20move%20to%20the%20hills.%20They%20started%20Brigadier's%20Cottage%20to%20share%20their%20organic%20life%20with%20others.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tailors%20to%20Roti%20Makers%3A%20How%20Indian%20Women%20Are%20Using%20Solar%20Energy%20To%20Earn%20a%20Livelihood%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20June%2C%20check%20out%20our%20%23ApnaGharSolar%20series%2C%20an%20exclusive%20deep%20dive%20by%20The%20Better%20India%20in%20collaboration%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.solarsquare.in%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsocialmedia%26utm_medium%3Dad%26utm_campaign%3DTheBetterIndia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESolarSquare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0on%20India%E2%80%99s%20solar%20power%20boom.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20more%20interesting%20stories%2C%20data%20and%20information!%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Learn%20from%20the%20success%20of%20countries%20like%20India%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20subhead%20in%20a%202024%20article%20by%20%3Cem%3EForbes%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20advised%2C%20as%20it%20urged%20readers%20and%20economies%20to%20pivot%20away%20from%20their%20dependency%20on%20non-renewable%20sources%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20article%20beckoned%20countries%20to%20take%20notes%20from%20India%E2%80%99s%20successful%20tryst%20with%20clean%20energy%2C%20it%20reasoned%20why.%20%E2%80%9CSince%202015%2C%20India%20has%20connected%2028%20million%20households%2C%20impacting%20120%20million%20people%2C%20to%20the%20electricity%20grids%20%E2%80%94%20a%20third%20of%20the%20global%20total%20during%20the%20last%20decade.%20In%20this%20duration%2C%20the%20country%20has%20also%20added%20more%20than%201%2C50%2C000%20MW%20of%20clean%20energy%20capacity%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20article%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20solar%20power%20being%20given%20a%20warm%20welcome%20from%20sectors%20ranging%20from%20education%20and%20healthcare%20to%20farming%20and%20small%20businesses%2C%20the%20country%20is%20seeing%20a%20profound%20shift%20in%20the%20way%20businesses%20are%20evolving%20to%20meet%20their%20energy%20requirements.%20And%20the%20statistics%20are%20telling.%20As%20the%20Global%20Electricity%20Review%202024%20noted%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20growth%20in%20solar%20generation%20in%202023%20pushed%20the%20country%20past%20Japan%20to%20become%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20third-largest%20solar%20power%20generator.%20It%20has%20climbed%20from%20ranking%20ninth%20in%202015.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%20is%20in%20clear%20sight%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20to%20achieve%20500%20GW%20of%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20by%202030.%20But%20as%20the%20energy%20transition%20is%20underway%20and%20industries%20hustle%20to%20do%20their%20bit%20to%20go%20solar%2C%20there%20are%20success%20stories%20emerging%20from%20pockets%20across%20India%20where%20households%2C%20farming%20entrepreneurs%2C%20and%20street%20vendors%20are%20championing%20a%20similar%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20take%20a%20look%20at%20the%20stories%20of%20some%20women%20who%20are%20using%20solar%20power%20to%20scale%20their%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Solar%20power%20for%20drying%20fruits%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Latika%20is%20a%20retired%20teacher%20who%20dived%20into%20the%20arena%20of%20solar%20power%20for%20farming%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-1-1718974537-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353854%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELatika%20is%20a%20retired%20teacher%20who%20dived%20into%20the%20arena%20of%20solar%20power%20for%20farming%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Ninad%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20a%20decade%20after%20the%20United%20Nations%20outlined%20the%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDGs)%20that%20formed%20a%20blueprint%20for%20the%20world%20to%20move%20towards%20a%20better%20future%2C%20farmers%20across%20Indian%20villages%20are%20acknowledging%20the%20power%20that%20clean%20energy%20holds.%20One%20such%20woman%20who%20has%20made%20solar%20power%20central%20to%20her%20business%20strategy%20is%20fourth-generation%20chikoo%20horticulturist%2C%20Latika%20Patil%20hailing%20from%20Dahanu%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20previously%2C%20the%20family%20sun-dried%20the%20fruits%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20proving%20conducive%20due%20to%20unpredictable%20weather%20patterns.%20This%20is%20when%20solar%20dryers%20came%20in.%20As%20Latika%E2%80%99s%20son%20Ninad%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20any%20climatic%20circumstances%2C%20the%20temperature%20of%20these%20plates%20is%20maintained%20at%2055%20to%2060%20degrees%2C%20which%20helps%20in%20conserving%20the%20nutrients.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20the%20plates%20are%20covered%20by%20UV%20protection%20high-grade%20polycarbonate%20sheets%2C%20which%20also%20protect%20the%20contents%20from%20dust%20and%20external%20particles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20profitability%20gained%20by%20venturing%20into%20solar%20drying%20is%20exponential%2C%20as%20Latika%20shares.%20Not%20only%20does%20it%20reduce%20the%20processing%20time%20of%20the%20fruit%20to%20one%20day%20compared%20to%20three%20to%20four%20days%2C%20she%20says%2C%20but%20it%20also%20increases%20the%20shelf-life%20to%20nine%20months%20from%20the%20previous%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fauragreenwellness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Solar%20power%20for%20running%20homestays%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%20is%20powered%20entirely%20by%20solar%20and%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20sustainability%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsolar-2-1718974568-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-353861%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%20is%20powered%20entirely%20by%20solar%20and%20is%20an%20ode%20to%20sustainability%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Nitin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20a%20stretch%20to%20say%20that%20the%20past%20decade%20has%20acted%20as%20an%20inflection%20point%20for%20solar%20power%20in%20the%20housing%20space.%20The%20idea%20gained%20explosive%20traction%2C%20and%20today%2C%20homeowners%20as%20well%20as%20those%20who%20have%20converted%20their%20spaces%20into%20homestays%2C%20are%20favouring%20solar%20power%20over%20traditional%20grid%20dependence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20solar%20panels%20can%20save%20you%20lakhs%20on%20electricity%20bills%20and%20prove%20a%20great%20investment%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20Media%20professional%20Shalini%20whose%20%E2%80%98Raison%20D%E2%80%99etre%E2%80%99%20is%20a%20beautiful%20homestay%20in%20Manali%2C%20recognised%20this%20potential%20early%20on.%20She%20along%20with%20her%20husband%20Nitin%20Beri%20are%20advocates%20of%20sustainable%20living%20and%20were%20keen%20that%20the%20homestay%20be%20a%20symbol%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShalini%20emphasises%20that%20they%20run%20their%20operations%20entirely%20on%20solar%20power%20and%20have%20a%20solar%20system%20in%20place%20that%20generates%20electricity%20on%20which%20the%20entire%20home%20runs.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20on%20days%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20as%20little%20as%2030%20percent%20sunlight%2C%20the%20system%20works%20efficiently.%20Additionally%2C%20any%20excess%20energy%20generated%20during%20the%20day%20is%20stored%20in%20batteries%2C%20which%20we%20then%20use%20for%20power%20backup%20when%20needed%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Nitin.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReach%20out%20to%20them%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fraisondetremanali%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Solar%20for%20street%20shops%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3